WEEK 11: SPEED (Go Syntax)

Weekly Goal: Learn Go fast (it's easier than Rust).

The Strategy:
Go is built for networking. Where Rust is complex, Go is brutally simple. We use it for anything that needs to handle 10,000 connections at once.

