Day 74 (Thu): Interfaces

Task: Learn implicit interfaces (Go's superpower).

Day 75 (Fri): Error Handling

Task: if err != nil. The Go mantra.

Day 76 (Sat): RAID - "Port Scanner" (v1)

Mission: Write a sequential port scanner in Go.

Observation: Notice how slow it is scanning 100 ports one by one.

